{"tid":2611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【以一敵四】遭4匪扑頭紮起 瑜伽導師自行鬆綁槍殺2賊","createTime":"2016-11-26T00:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-26T00:26:04.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c64820a3d18c9ca327ccf7a0791ec066eba2b86a","tid":2611,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"<strong>【以一敵四】遭4匪扑頭紮起 瑜伽導師自行鬆綁槍殺2賊</strong><br />\n<br />\n2016-11-26 07:43:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n智利四名劫匪闖入一名瑜伽女導師的寓所，把她綁起後搜掠財物，但事主自行鬆綁，開槍擊斃兩名劫匪，另兩人落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n遇劫的瑜伽導師卡莎(Hari Khalsa)，61歲，原居於美國德薩斯州，1979年移居智利。在本周四，四名劫匪潛入她於聖地亞哥市郊的寓所，用武器痛擊她的頭部，然後將她綁起。<br />\n<br />\n不過，卡莎稍後自行鬆綁，拿出暗藏枕頭下的手槍，開槍打死兩名劫匪，另兩人逃去。警方說，由於卡莎是自衛殺人，所以不會被起訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3522ba21871f5ac24cf77934b6666e38c83d769f","tid":2611,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:09:21.000Z","msg":"mission impossible<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bce50fe4dc8a50aab38db7ce503766c66c3fae","tid":2611,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:11:56.000Z","msg":"高登女user<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7792a64c553132f876529986c738efa6d9864048","tid":2611,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T00:26:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}